Meat Loaf

1 pound ground beef
1/2 cup dry bread crumbs
1/4 cup and 1 teaspoon diced onion
1/4 cup green pepper
1/4 cup celery 
1 teaspoon garlic powderâ€¨1/4 teaspoon salt
(can substitute 1/2 teaspoon garlic salt for both)
1/4 teaspoon ground black pepper

Combine beef, bread crumbs, onion, garlic powder, salt, and pepper until evenly blended.
Shape the mixture into a loaf and place in a glass or metal pan which has been buttered or coated with oil 

Put in oven at 375 for 1 hour 
